Package: project2026
Title: Statistical Analysis of Height, Weight and Physical Activity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given   = "Your",
      family  = "Name",
      email   = "your.name@students.mq.edu.au",
      role    = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "")
    )
Description: Provides wrapper functions for three statistical analyses
    performed on the project2026 dataset: (1) simple linear regression of
    weight on height, (2) an independent-samples t-test comparing mean
    heights across genders, and (3) a chi-square test of independence
    between gender and physical activity level.  Each wrapper returns a
    structured list with a custom S3 print() method.
